01:02:07.389 --> 01:02:11.074
I build this tank,
and maybe there's some water in

01:02:11.074 --> 01:02:14.159
the lake here at the foot of the
tank,

01:02:14.159 --> 01:02:17.492
and I go to the top,
and go to the top and empty

01:02:17.492 --> 01:02:21.820
little buckets until I've got
some water at the big height.

01:02:21.820 --> 01:02:26.110
Then I've done some work and
it'll pay me back when I open

01:02:26.110 --> 01:02:28.820
the tap and let it all rush
down,

01:02:28.820 --> 01:02:33.708
and it may turn a turbine blade
and give me back thermo electric

01:02:33.708 --> 01:02:34.329
power.
 

01:02:34.329 --> 01:02:36.800
You want to do similar things
electrically.

01:02:36.800 --> 01:02:40.179
You want to invest with some
work and it'll give you back.

01:02:40.179 --> 01:02:43.583
So one thing I can do is I can
take a plus and minus charge

01:02:43.583 --> 01:02:46.869
which love to be next to each
other and separate them.

01:02:46.869 --> 01:02:50.552
Now, I've done some work,
